From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*pyaw||swim, float, raft}} (STEDT; {{zh-ref|Benedict, 1972}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

:Inside Chinese, cognate with {{och-l|浮|to float}}, {{och-l|柎|raft}}, {{och-l|泭}} & {{och-l|桴|raft, beam}};
:Outside Chinese, cognate with {{cog|bo|འཕྱོ་བ|t=swim, float, soar}}, & {{cog|kac|tr=pyau ~ byau|t=fly, float; play, shoot, as a fish}}.

